abstract: Agnieszka Radwanska bagged the biggest title of her young career Saturday afternoon in Tokyo, defeating Vera Zvonareva, 6-3, 6-2, to win the Toray Pan Pacific Open.
snippet: Agnieszka Radwanska bagged the biggest title of her young career Saturday afternoon in Tokyo, defeating Vera Zvonareva, 6-3, 6-2, to win the Toray Pan Pacific Open.
lead_paragraph: Agnieszka Radwanska bagged the biggest title of her young career Saturday afternoon in Tokyo, defeating Vera Zvonareva, 6-3, 6-2, to win the Toray Pan Pacific Open in Ariake Coliseum.
